{"tid":1908611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土派唔壯大，進攻立法會係死路一條","createTime":"2020-03-03T11:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T01:42:47.000Z","uid":189739,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d04a33a5ed6e69626349fccaf856483db04ebf11","tid":1908611,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:41:31.000Z","msg":"首先，我係支持議會外抗爭為首，議會外抗爭為次。<br />\n<br />\n過去八個月勇武崛起，抗爭以街頭為首，議會為輔助進行，成功打破販民三十年內，一直以道德光環掩飾，內裡關鍵棄權，出賣香港嘅局面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月勇武地下化，加上販民工會大力推動功能組別，代表我哋而家行緊議會內抗爭為首，議會外為次嘅路。<br />\n<br />\n議會就係大台，議會內抗爭就係爭做大台。本土派唔壯大，只會比暗共販民騎劫，又係會「循序漸進」地去死。只會重返販民三十年內，一直以光環掩飾，內裡關鍵棄權，出賣香港嘅局面。不過今次個光環係由勇武嘅血，本土嘅肉組成。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講販民係好人，幾個月前話咩「大人去罷工，細佬唔洗衝」，一定要組織工會搞罷工。成三個月喇，民陣為首嘅十幾個工會又唔罷工。甚至醫護罷工嘅時候，連一個其他工會都唔follow，淨係叫人做功能組別選民，你哋唔覺得有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n販民罄竹難書，賣港賊比比皆是：白頭佬唔做立法會主席，比左梁君彥做；周偉雄酒後話冇支持過d後生仔；楊岳僑在美國面前，偷換五大訴求普選做林鄭下台，伙葉建源游說美國將人權法嚴重減辣。最可笑係白頭佬同周偉雄最後以四千幾票對二千幾贏左區議會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋或者會講佢哋唔代表販民，仲有鄺神呢？鄺神係販民嘅異類，從來都冇埋過堆。你有冇見過劉慧卿坐喺佢單車後面？鄺神每一次出嚟都係自己一個。販民唔會變，只會繼續賣港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直選係講全部人嘅共同意識，係全香港選民嘅意識。選舉過後，議會抗爭係講最大派嘅共同意識，係少數人嘅意識。因為要贏要全部人同意，輸只需少數人關鍵棄權，所謂的共同意識係由販民元老決定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比之下，梁天琦入獄後本土派一沉不振，本土行動係好壯大，但由於只在議會外抗爭，本土意識仲係好幼嫩。好多香港人其實仲未真正地思想醒覺。如果要支持進攻功能組別，本土意識必須在思想上真正開花，本土派必須成民主派內最大派。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9e21c104c96cc1e4ffe1457089d76881879820","tid":1908611,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:42:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65da28f5b3954a7042ced3e94bc0f8f238138434","tid":1908611,"uid":290739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:42:46.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b17d098d30526e7981028d4aef80557c0502b66","tid":1908611,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1bece324a4a156190b58ea78d49849ba5b3ec8","tid":1908611,"uid":172192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8896cd7c9703bc71a465429dd725137f10aa20b7","tid":1908611,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a8bc60989ad5af39ed944ea7f2efd192bf5ba9","tid":1908611,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31951dbcef97f4b88baa0edfa0f271b5520ff901","tid":1908611,"uid":347404,"like"