img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該係議會外為首，議會內輔助"},{"pid":"89e8a60ba945f42d93e77c1f6199a646e345756f","tid":1908611,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:51:35.000Z","msg":"點壯大先"},{"pid":"86ace9236b8cbe84ea696ab4357531e3c126f5c0","tid":1908611,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3bfce7f4be50670b000e43cf04dc9858175ee8","tid":1908611,"uid":56904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"又一個2016年訓著咗既人...<br />\n選舉主任個關呢 宣誓DQ呢<br />\n<br />\n4年前大家已經知道本土派/獨派永遠都入唔到議會<br />\n只能夠做議會外既抗爭<br />\n依家又拎返出黎 又要再衰多次先死心?"},{"pid":"c132a8f954dd1a000549f14e426c472b38a5e3a9","tid":1908611,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa218d64468d2c14adcf47a99b789e1829ff58c6","tid":1908611,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"神獸會鶳賣港議員"},{"pid":"9b34419a647f4dea707dba5b31781892399284a4","tid":1908611,"uid":189739,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd3bfce7f4be50670b000e43cf04dc9858175ee8","tid":1908611,"uid":56904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"又一個2016年訓著咗既人...<br />\n選舉主任個關呢 宣誓DQ呢<br />\n<br />\n4年前大家已經知道本土派/獨派永遠都入唔到議會<br />\n只能夠做議會外既抗爭<br />\n依家又拎返出黎 又要再衰多次先死心?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:55:54.000Z","msg":"完全同意，不過太多人都扮唔知到... <br />\n<br />\n事實上立法會係死路，不過寧願本土派比人DQ，好過暗共販民扮做野...."},{"pid":"225f27396768264a03c868b1a3774c8c3f961535","tid":1908611,"uid":206386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac18335f4e46e1ebba9e961cbfb0eaa1e5aeaf74","tid":1908611,"uid":189739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T11:59:4